creator: Translate Apps
descriptionHtml:
English Hindi Dictionary, This is an absolutely freeware and fully offline English to Hindi Dictionary.

English Hindi Dictionary in the smallest app size with about 150000 words.

No need anymore for a translator or friend for translation English to Hindi.

Our English to Hindi dictionary works in OFFLINE mode. No internet connection is required after the app download. So you can carry this dictionary with you everywhere in your cellphone for use when you have no net connection.

This app is a quick dictionary and thesaurus with English to Hindi meanings for almost all words.

It provides the trusted English to Hindi Word meanings with the Android experience.

History & Favourites/Bookmark Options.

Word Suggestion Support.

This will be helpful to find out the meaning of any word.

When you start typing, you will see some words starting with the letters you typed. The dictionary searches in a database for the matching words.

Word Clear Button.

- Low memory usage and small size.
- FREE Downloads
- Easy to use simple app interface with new look and feel.
- works very well in offline
- Voice Search - Speak to search a word.
- Pronounce & Voice Search
- Fast and easy to use
- Share Words
- Copy Words
- Auto Suggestion


Thanks for your valuable support,feedback and suggestions.
